": "Maybe an upper limit of 80 or so?\n\nSimple qualification rule:\n\nTerm for which a person is running must end no later than 180 days after that candidate's 80th birthday.\n\nAdmittedly, Chuck Grassley has remained healthy and lucent well into advance age, but that is not the norm.\n\nThurmond, Byrd, Feinstein, McConnell, etc prove there needs to be an age limit.\n\nHow many of you would board a commercial airliner w/ two 80-yr old pilots?\n\nHow many would have surgery performed by an 80-yr old surgeon?", "author": "dataonly", "created": 1783691204906, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "empiretc", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "There Needs to Be An Age Limit on Serving in Congress", "last_comment_created": 1783692075278, "content": "<p>Maybe an upper limit of 80 or so?</p>\n<p>Simple qualification rule:</p>\n<p>Term for which a person is running must end no later than 180 days after that candidate's 80th birthday.</p>\n<p>Admittedly, Chuck Grassley has remained healthy and lucent well into advance age, but that is not the norm.</p>\n<p>Thurmond, Byrd, Feinstein, McConnell, etc prove there needs to be an age limit.</p>\n<p>How many of you would board a commercial airliner w/ two 80-yr old pilots?</p>\n<p>How many would have surgery performed by an 80-yr old surgeon?</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 1, "score_up": 13, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2075250044018553207", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_vid